Summary: Was taking pictures of sky later observed a dot in the image.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside taking pictures of the sky. Later I observed a black dot in this picture. When I enlarged it the black dot seems to have an aura. This is the first I have observed. The dot is in area near where the sun is behind the clouds.
